metadata.title: Doomer
metadata.description: Doomers is a collection of 667 Non-Fungible Tokens on the ethereum network that will be the only survivors remain when the inevitable DOOM strikes us. The contract and supporting infrastructure have been designed to maximize the distribution of ownership and allow for holders of the tokens to have a voting right in how the project develops and evolves. The project attempts to to design a community focused on exploring new artistâ€™s styles through future generations while using multiple tokens types and other blockchain offerings to empower its owners.
